<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656633' id='t-656633'>Or take Korea, at the other end of the spectrum.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658761' id='t-658761'>In the year 2000, Korea did already very well,</span>
