<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689723' id='t-689723'>A major overhaul of Poland's education</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692309' id='t-692309'>helped to dramatically reduce between variability among schools,</span>
